Resource Profile: CH EPREG RelatedPerson: Parent

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-epreg/StructureDefinition/ch-epreg-relatedperson-parent Version: 1.0.0-ballot
Active as of 2025-05-22 Computable Name: ChEpregRelatedPersonParent

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

This profile constrains the RelatedPerson resource to represent the relationship between the parent (besides the biological mother) and the child.

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: CH EPREG Composition
